1. Define the environment variable SETI_GBT to the location of this package, e.g. export SETI_GBT=/usr/local/src/SETI_GBT

2. Install CFITSIO (http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/fitsio/)

3. Edit $SETI_GBT/src/Makefile as needed.

4. cd $SETI_GBT/src; make; make clean  (Note: Depending on your system, you may have to set LD_RUN_PATH to properly link slalib.)


